title: Focus on the process
desc: Focus on the process, not just the end result. Don't just focus on the end result of becoming a successful coder, but also on the process of learning and improving your coding skills. Celebrate your small victories along the way, and don't be too hard on yourself if you experience setbacks or failures.
metadesc: Don't just focus on the end result of becoming a successful coder
author: CharGpt
